---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Banking & Finance Security Solutions">

<main class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen">

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24 text-center">

<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-blue-400">
Banking & Finance Cybersecurity Solutions
</h1>

<p class="mt-4 text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
Protect financial transactions, detect fraud, and secure customer data and payment systems.
</p>

</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24">

<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-8 text-center">
Key Security Requirements for Banking
</h2>

<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Fraud Detection & Transaction Monitoring</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Real-time analytics and monitoring to detect anomalous transactions and fraudulent behavior.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: Trellix</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Data Loss Prevention</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Protect customer financial data and sensitive records from exfiltration.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: Forcepoint</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Endpoint Detection</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Protect workstations and servers from advanced endpoint threats.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: SentinelOne</p>
</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Privileged Access Management</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Secure administrative accounts and privileged workflows across banking systems.</p>
<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-400">Recommended OEM: ARCON</p>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24">
<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-blue-400 mb-8 text-center">Recommended OEM Vendors</h2>
<div class="grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Trellix</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Threat detection and advanced analytics for financial environments.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">Forcepoint</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Data protection and DLP for customer data and transaction records.</p>
</div>
<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">
<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">ARCON</h3>
<p class="mt-2 text-gray-300 text-sm">Privileged access management for banking administrative systems.</p>
</div>
</div>
</section>

</main>

</Layout>
